headline: Astrana Health, Inc. (ASTH) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Lag Estimates
summary: Astrana Health, Inc. (ASTH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -39.13% and 2.33%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
